title: Winds of the Wasteland (John Wayne, 1936) Western | Full Length Movie

sources.title: Winds of the Wasteland (John Wayne, 1936) Western | Full Length Movie
sources.description:
A six-shooter writes the law as war flames on the range! Adventure---as bullets blaze the pioneer trail!
The arrival of the telegraph put Pony Express riders like John Blair and his pal Smoky out of work. A race will decide whether they or stageline owner Drake get the government mail contract.

Director: Mack V. Wright
Writers: Joseph F. Poland,
Stars: John Wayne, Phyllis Fraser, Lew Kelly 
Genres: Comedy, Romance, Western
